query: SELECT COUNT(*) as total_duplicate_images, SUM(property_count) as total_duplicate_assignments FROM (SELECT image_url, COUNT(DISTINCT property_id) as property_count FROM property_images GROUP BY image_url HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT property_id) > 1) as duplicates;
